<br>
<br>
Comparing a game that you pick up, get obsessed with, then 5-10months later abandon, to a medical illness is absurb and laughable, and anyone who buys into that is retarded.<br>
<br>
I'd compare it more to really falling head over heals with a new girl, cant get her off ur mind for a few months , then  you fuck her a few times and you are sick of her. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=maneta@thesaryrntavern>Maneta</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style='color:yellow;'>Tavern Ale Swiller</span></span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(6/20/03 10:53 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3321.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> eq addiction</span><hr size=1> note to self: never go on a date with Loftel <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ratsan>Ratsan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><span style='color:blue;'>Tavern Regular</span></span><br>  Posts: 231<br> <font color=#6FB8DD>(6/20/03 11:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3321.topic&index=12>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://stateofthegame.50megs.com/mov/demon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: eq addiction</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>&quot;Man, I sure am tired of this crack, It's just not good anymore, I think I'm going to quit it&quot;. You don't hear diehard gamblers talking about how gambling &quot;used&quot; to be fun, and they are n